ZH: 昨天发生了一起严重的空难。
EN: Yesterday a serious air disaster occurred.

ZH: 空难造成了很多人员伤亡。
EN: The air disaster caused many casualties.

ZH: 这次空难的原因尚未确定。
EN: The cause of this air disaster is still under investigation.

ZH: 空难发生在深夜，飞机坠毁在山谷里。
EN: The air disaster happened in the late night, with the plane crashing in a valley.

ZH: 航空公司的首席执行官发布了一份声明，表示对空难事件深感悲痛。
EN: The CEO of the airline issued a statement expressing deep sorrow over the air disaster.

ZH: 救援人员正在空难现场进行搜索和救援工作。
EN: Rescue workers are conducting search and rescue operations at the site of the air disaster.

ZH: 这次空难导致了广泛的公众关注。
EN: This air disaster has attracted widespread public attention.

ZH: 幸存者们讲述了空难发生时的惊险经历。
EN: Survivors recounted the harrowing experience of the air disaster.

ZH: 空难调查委员会将对此事件展开周密调查。
EN: The air disaster investigation committee will conduct a thorough investigation into the incident.

ZH: 华为集团失去了多名员工在这次空难中遇难。
EN: Huawei lost several employees in this air disaster.

ZH: 遗属们表达了对空难遇难者的哀思。
EN: The families of the victims expressed their grief for those who perished in the air disaster.

ZH: 空难发生后，航空公司遵循了相关的应急处理程序。
EN: Following the air disaster, the airline followed the relevant emergency procedures.

ZH: 乘客们在遭遇空难时都表现得十分勇敢。
EN: The passengers showed great courage when they faced the air disaster.

ZH: 空难给飞机制造厂带来了巨大的负面影响。
EN: The air disaster had a huge negative impact on the aircraft manufacturing plant.

ZH: 机组人员的英勇举动在空难中挽救了许多乘客的生命。
EN: The heroic actions of the crew saved many passengers' lives in the air disaster.

ZH: 受到空难影响，公司的股价有所下跌。
EN: The company's stock price has dropped due to the influence of the air disaster.

ZH: 空难成了当地媒体报道的焦点。
EN: The air disaster became the focus of local media coverage.

ZH: 飞行员在空难中表现得十分专业。
EN: The pilot showed great professionalism during the air disaster.

ZH: 空难给乘客们留下了深刻的心理阴影。
EN: The air disaster left a deep psychological scar on the passengers.

ZH: 拯救幸存者是救援人员的首要任务之一。
EN: Rescuing survivors is one of the primary tasks for rescue workers in the aftermath of an air disaster.
